data.description: Luxurious private estate with all the amenities situated on just over 11 acres and only minutes from the city.  The property features well appointed main house, over garage apartment, separate in-law residence, pool, massive outdoor living area, steam shower in the master bath, workout studio, storm shelter and a 30x40 outbuilding for all the toys.  Craftmanship throughout.  Don't miss out on this one!
